e\cdot a=10+2i
\frac e {\bar a} =\frac{5+i}4
a\cdot \bar a=\frac{4(10+2i)}{5+i}=8\cdot \frac{5+i}{5+i}=8
a=x+iy, \bar a=x-iy,
a\cdot \bar a=(x+iy)(x-iy)=x^2+y^2=\mid a\mid ^2
\mid a\mid ^2=8\implies |a|=2\sqrt2 
e\cdot a=10+2i, \mid e\cdot a \mid=\sqrt{10^2+2^2}=\sqrt {104}
\mid e\cdot a \mid= \mid e\mid\cdot \mid a \mid, 
\mid e\mid\cdot \mid a \mid= \sqrt {104}
\mid a \mid=\sqrt 8,
\mid e\mid=\frac{\sqrt{104}}{\sqrt{8}}=\sqrt{13}
